         <abstract id="aspace_9c6275dcc1ad075d36830fbaf7386acf">Mounted black and white photographs, each labeled Biblioteca Domingo Carles Tolrá, Barcelona; in pencil: name of artist, date, title, collection; Most mounts stamped: "A questa proba es copia d'un negatiu propietat del "ARXIV MAS" i no pot ser reproduida sens permis"; Many photographs indexed to Post (A History of Spanish Painting by Chandler Rathfon Post, 14 v. in 20, Harvard-Radcliffe fine arts series, Cambridge, Mass., Harvard University Press, 1930-66); also 264 undivided miscellaneous Spanish painting, architecture and sculpture.</abstract>
      </did>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_arest">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <userestrict id="aspace_urest">
