      </userestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_cite">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Miscellaneous Spanish Painting, Architecture and Sculpture</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_sc">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Mounted black and white photographs, each labeled Biblioteca Domingo Carles Tolrá, Barcelona; in pencil: name of artist, date, title, collection; Most mounts stamped: "A questa proba es copia d'un negatiu propietat del "ARXIV MAS" i no pot ser reproduida sens permis"; Many photographs indexed to Post (A History of Spanish Painting by Chandler Rathfon Post, 14 v. in 20, Harvard-Radcliffe fine arts series, Cambridge, Mass., Harvard University Press, 1930-66); also 264 undivided miscellaneous Spanish painting, architecture and sculpture.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_arr1">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>10 boxes with each artist organized by labeled dividers. Boxes 9 and 10 contain 264 undivided miscellaneous Spanish painting, architecture and sculpture.</p>  
      </arrangement>
